{"tid":2275853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰空姐流淚撕不平等合約 嘆次次都同公司共渡時艱 但公司賺錢嗰陣就冇同過我哋分享","createTime":"2020-11-07T12:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T12:01:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"32a752ee884d2e997a2781af0d10b8686e5343b1","tid":2275853,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ckojkcUON9c18LYAqNwoB3D5RwY=/802x687/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G6LDG7HTAFF2BHMB7S2KWWEYPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FckojkcUON9c18LYAqNwoB3D5RwY%3D%2F802x687%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG6LDG7HTAFF2BHMB7S2KWWEYPM.jpg&h=a0b73dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰要求倖存員工簽署不平等新合約，有國泰空姐在昨日凌晨限期屆滿後於社交平台上發佈相片，身穿國泰空姐制服，四周紙碎飛花，寫上「由一出呢份約開始，我已經好想撕爛佢」。空姐Apple（化名）表示，拍下相片並發佈網上，除了紀念一套對其別具意義的制服外，同時藉相片表達對國泰不滿，「出呢張合約根本唔想留我哋」，對國泰做法感到憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n任職國泰空姐十多年的Apple，在其ig賬戶上發帖說：「由一出呢份約開始，我已經好想撕爛佢。」帖文配圖是一張她身穿國泰制服、四周紙碎四散的相片。她說拍照時忍不住流下眼淚，在航空生涯最不捨是一班好同事，但終於要各奔前程：「I&rsquo;m moving on with my life（我會繼續我的生活）」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/GUFFC25MFVHXVEKU6BXYVWWPZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FGUFFC25MFVHXVEKU6BXYVWWPZI%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=965edecc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FGUFFC25MFVHXVEKU6BXYVWWPZI%2F&h=9a497ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/GUFFC25MFVHXVEKU6BXYVWWPZI/</a>"},{"pid":"d8547ab74b0ccac2d07da72288e23daca4aecbd2","tid":2275853,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T13:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/